@deftypefn {Function File} {} com2str (@var{zz}, @var{flg})
This function has been deprecated.  Use num2str instead.

Convert complex number to a string.
@strong{Inputs}
@table @var
@item zz
complex number
@item flg
format flag
0 (default):            -1, 0, 1,   1i,   1 + 0.5i
1 (for use with zpout): -1, 0, + 1, + 1i, + 1 + 0.5i
@end table
@end deftypefn
